messages.speaker: agent
messages.text: Hello! I'm Anita Bhargava, strategic financial advisor and co-founder of Bharosa Club. I'm excited to explore your financial journey together and help you build a sustainable wealth strategy that aligns with your values and aspirations. Today, we'll focus on understanding your lifestyle - both current and desired - to create a foundation for our future discussions. This personalized approach will help us develop strategies that truly reflect your unique goals. Let's start with the basics - could you please tell me your name and age?
